WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.012 --> 00:00:04.350
If you said they'd weigh the same, great work. Dividing by 2 on both sides gives

00:00:04.362 --> 00:00:08.735
me 4 pounds. Notice that when I've been solving these problems, I keep my equals

00:00:08.747 --> 00:00:13.060
sign lined up in the center. And after every time I perform an operation on both

00:00:13.072 --> 00:00:17.375
sides, I draw a line. This helps me organize my work and my thoughts. Make sure

00:00:17.387 --> 00:00:21.435
that you can do this or organize your thoughts in some manner when you go to

00:00:21.447 --> 00:00:22.265
solve problems.

